   STOLEN-COP-CARS (San Francisco) _ A brazen car thief has been
stealing unmarked cop cars _ and police have been slow to notice.
Since Memorial Day, three undercover police cars have been swiped
from a city lot near the Hall of Justice. But the department failed
to realize two of the cars were missing for a week or more, and one
of them was used to commit a minor crime. By JIM HERRON ZAMORA.
