and family planning groups host a policy forum addressing the
HIV/AIDS crisis in Sub-Saharan Africa. Henry Foster, chairman of
the U.S. Committee for the United Nations Population Fund is among
those participating. This story will likely focus on the AIDS
orphans issue. Developing. (Michals, Cox News Service). 15.
</P>
