<P>
   ENTERTAINMENT-ARTS
</P>
<P>
   SURVIVOR _ Why hasn't anyone blabbed the winner of ``Survivor?''
Each contestant has a carrot and a stick, finanically, in their
contract to help them keep quiet. Plus, says producer Mark Burnett,
they've all been through a bonding experience that makes them want
to keep it a secret, despite tabloid offers. (Kloer, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 12.
</P>
