<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-20 14:05 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9483 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f BC-TECH-ROUNDUP-BOS &LR;      06-20 0705
