   WINETALK (Undated) _ The weekly wine column: Sancerres and
Sancerre wannabes. By Frank J. Prial.
</P>
<P>
   TASTINGS (Undated) _ Gewurtztraminers. By Frank J. Prial. By
Eric Asimov.
</P>
