   PAINS OF THE WEEKEND ATHLETE: Weekend Warrior Season is in full
swing, that time of year when cooped-up big boys and girls suddenly
burst onto tennis courts, ball fields, golf courses and bicycle
lanes. It's also the time of year when doctors, physical
therapists, athletic trainers, chiropractors and even
acupuncturists tend to middle-aged recreational athletes who
typically play too hard, too quickly. (Includes 4-column color
