store here. The new maternity collection, which debuted in March,
is a basics-oriented, somewhat-limited selection of Gap-style
separates, including T-shirts, capris and cardigans, most in solid
colors such as tan, black and white that make them great wardrobe
staples for mixing and matching.
</P>
<P>
   Don't miss: Ruffled dress ($58) in matte jersey material; great
for lazy summer days.
</P>
