</P>
<P>
   SITE: justbabies.com
</P>
<P>
   What you'll find: The maternity collection features classic
staples provided by vendors such as L'attesa and Belly Basics. Like
gap.com, the selection is limited, but the items offered are solid,
classic pieces that make for great wardrobe variety.
</P>
<P>
   Don't miss: Leapin Leopard Diaper Bag set, $170. This
three-piece set is great for moms who want to add a little zing to
