<P>
   BASKETBALL
</P>
<P>
   BKN-LAKERS-FOLO _ Follow story on Lakers winning NBA title. They
have MVP Shaq, they have Kobe, but most of the credit goes to coach
Phil Jackson, who won his 7th NBA title as a coach and ninth
overall. (Bunn, Atlanta Jourtnal-Constitution). 18.
</P>
<P>
   BASEBALL
</P>
<P>
   BBO-BASEBALL-RESEARCH _ WEST PALM BEACH, Fla. _ You think
Trekkies are bad, wait til you get a load of the baseball nuts
descending on West Palm Beach for a weekend homage to baseball. The
Society for American Baseball Research convention lineup includes
presentations on Italian baseball, Baseball Songs and Poems.
(Capozzi, Palm Beach Post). 30. WITH ILLUSTRATION.
</P>
<P>
   FOOTBALL
</P>
<P>
   FBC-UGA-STADIUM _ ATHENS, Ga. _ The University of Georgia will
begin the process of laying new sod in Sanford Stadium, the last
step in a six-month long, $1 million renovation project that was
the result of a brown, foul-smelling liquid that began seeping up
through the ground last year. The Bulldogs' timing is not good,
however, in the middle of a drought and with Athens-Clarke County
in the grip of water restrictions. (Brice, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 6.
</P>
<P>
   GOLF
</P>
