<P>
   TIGER WOODS TRIBUTE PAGE _ In recognition of Tiger Wood's
remarkable performance in the U.S. Open over the weekend, CoxNet
has prepared a special tribute page in tribute to the golfer's
15-stroke victory at Pebble Beach. The page, available in full
color, features three photos of Woods, a copy of his scorecard
results for Sunday's amazing round, and some facts on the U.S Open.
The page is built in a modular format with space for a 6 column by
3-inch ad on the bottom. The page is available now by using the
Budget Tool, with a run date of Tuesday, June 20, with a category
of Sports and a subcategory of Golf. It is also still good for use
on Wednesday or later. The page can also be found on the Cox Server
in the Sports Folder. For more information, contact CoxNet at 404
525-5456.
</P>
