<P>
   MADDEN-ARREST (Undated) _ Last week, Steve Madden was a
celebrity designer, whose cutting-edge platform shoes appeared on
well-watched teens like Melissia Joan Hart (star of Sabrina),
Leanne Rimes, Ivanka Trump, Michelle Geller, Ricki Lake and Chelsea
