wrongful death lawsuit against federal agents include grim
descriptions of the government's 1993 raid and siege at the Branch
Davidian compound and pictures and videotape of some of the
children who were killed. The first witness says sect members had
no plans to ambush the government agents when they arrived to serve
a warrant. By JIM HENDERSON.
